<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        .confirmation-container {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .confirmation-container h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #1f8b4c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .confirmation-container p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .mechanic-image {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: url('https://img.icons8.com/clouds/100/000000/mechanic.png') no-repeat center center;
            background-size: cover;
        }

        .thank-you-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #1f8b4c;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .thank-you-button:hover {
            background-color: #166534;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="confirmation-container">
    <div class="mechanic-image"></div>
    <h1>Thank You for Choosing Us!</h1>
    <p>Your booking has been placed successfully. Our mechanic will reach you soon.</p>
    <p>We appreciate your trust in our service.</p>
    <a href="book" class="thank-you-button">Back</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
